<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="id"><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><title>Serah Terima Barang</title><style>body{font-family:DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#111827}.title{text-align:center;font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:4px}.subtitle{text-align:center;margin-bottom:24px}table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin-bottom:16px}th,td{border:1px solid #374151;padding:6px;vertical-align:top}.no-border td{border:none;padding:3px 0}.signature{margin-top:48px}.signature td{border:none;text-align:center;height:90px}.small{font-size:10px;color:#4b5563}</style></head><body><div class="title">BERITA ACARA SERAH TERIMA BARANG IT</div><div class="subtitle">Nomor Dokumen: {{ $goodsIssue->document_no }}</div><table class="no-border"><tr><td style="width:160px">Nomor Transaksi</td><td>: {{ $goodsIssue->issue_no }}</td></tr><tr><td>Tanggal</td><td>: {{ $goodsIssue->issue_date?->format('d/m/Y') }}</td></tr><tr><td>Lokasi Asal</td><td>: {{ $goodsIssue->sourceLocation?->name ?? '-' }}</td></tr><tr><td>Lokasi Tujuan</td><td>: {{ $goodsIssue->targetLocation?->name ?? '-' }}</td></tr><tr><td>Penerima</td><td>: {{ $goodsIssue->recipient_name }}</td></tr><tr><td>Departemen</td><td>: {{ $goodsIssue->recipient_department ?? '-' }}</td></tr><tr><td>PIC Penyerah</td><td>: {{ $goodsIssue->picUser?->name ?? '-' }}</td></tr></table><p>Telah dilakukan serah terima barang IT dengan rincian sebagai berikut:</p><table><thead><tr><th>No</th><th>Nama Barang</th><th>Qty</th><th>Serial</th><th>Kondisi</th><th>Catatan</th></tr></thead><tbody>@foreach($goodsIssue->items as $line)<tr><td>{{ $loop->iteration }}</td><td>{{ $line->item?->name ?? '-' }}<br><span class="small">Kode: {{ $line->item?->sku ?? '-' }}</span></td><td>{{ $line->qty }}</td><td>{{ $line->serial_no ?? '-' }}</td><td>{{ strtoupper($line->condition_status) }}</td><td>{{ $line->notes ?? '-' }}</td></tr>@endforeach</tbody></table><p>Barang tersebut telah diterima dalam kondisi sebagaimana tercantum pada tabel di atas.</p><table class="signature"><tr><td>Yang Menyerahkan,<br><br><br><br><strong>{{ $goodsIssue->picUser?->name ?? '.........................' }}</strong><br>PIC IT / Gudang</td><td>Yang Menerima,<br><br><br><br><strong>{{ $goodsIssue->recipient_name }}</strong><br>Penerima Barang</td></tr></table></body></html>
